snippet.title: KEG WARS :: Studio Tour
snippet.description: Keg Wars is a innovative tactical take on the classic TicTacToe game. In Keg Wars instead of crosses or circles, players chose cards with different abilities to dominate the game board and achieve a three-in-a-row winning scenario. Keg Wars is also the Bronze Award Winner in Comic Con! Powered by GameNest® and PlayStation® First.
